{
  "stem": "6130.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Downstairs was my mother-in-law who was living.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Of course, she died in Auschwitz, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And upstairs, my husband and I were living.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they wouldn't let me in there either.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I looked to the door.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I could see my kitchen furniture.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They wouldn't let me in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very well.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very well.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We-- in the ghetto, we had something like a governing body.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe that's the wrong expression.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they were in charge to take care of get everything to go right in the ghetto, you know, nobody should escape.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Oh, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I have to go back to that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My youngest brother did one night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- they were in communication with the SS, or the Hungarian Arrow Cross.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was the Hungarian SS.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they were told that we have to get ready, that the following day, we will be transported.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We had to go to the temple.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Close to the temple was the Jewish elementary school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That was a-- I don't remember-- two, three, or four story, big building.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that's where we had to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So we all got together-- and we were told what you can have.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Just a little package.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we started to hide a few things-- sewing in shoulder pads in our coats.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was in summer, but we knew we have to be prepared for winter.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] toothpaste, we put in gold chain, in toothpaste, or in gold pin and some Hungarian money, which we didn't know if it was good for anything.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that's what they did, and underwear and some shoes, something lightweight so we could carry.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But I remember vaguely that there was like a wagon we pulled somethings to the-- to that school.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
